	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I believe EPROM and Flash are really similar, actually (the underlying technology).  But I did notice and just checked, the SST39SF series Flash claims "greater than 100 years data retention".  AMD Flashroms claim 20 years at 125 degrees C (that's 250+ Fahrenheit), I'm sure it would last quite a while at room temperature.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
