		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Flash is way to go, they're usually cheaper and easier to find, at least for me. Pinouts are same aswell, and you can easily reprogram one if something goes whack.
<br />As for what to use, get whatever your programmer uses. I prefer 5V only flash chips, which seem to be mostly 49F, though its not a rule. Just check datasheets before buying.

		

		</td>
